headline: SOUTHWEST AIRLINES ANNOUNCES REALIGNMENT OF BOARD SIZE
summary: Southwest Airlines (NYSE: LUV) today announced that Directors David Cush and Gregg Saretsky have informed the Company that they are stepping off the Board effective Feb. 23, 2026.

headline: Rotation Lifts Energy 23% as Tech Slips Since Oct. 28
summary: Investors rotate from crowded tech into energy, materials, and industrials as market leadership begins to broaden.
